00:11:29,319 --> 00:11:31,800
but we also must understand that God

184
00:11:31,800 --> 00:11:36,040
has defined how we are to worship Him.

185
00:11:36,040 --> 00:11:37,760
We understand that and we see that

186
00:11:37,760 --> 00:11:39,160
through the passage of Scripture

187
00:11:39,160 --> 00:11:41,080
that is referenced in Hebrews 11

