00:12:55,479 --> 00:12:58,160
in the process of time how they would bring forth

222
00:12:58,160 --> 00:12:59,440
these offerings.

223
00:12:59,440 --> 00:13:02,800
And we find that the offerings differed greatly.

224
00:13:02,800 --> 00:13:05,639
We find that the one offering that is mentioned

225
00:13:05,639 --> 00:13:08,440
in verse number three, the offering of Cain

226
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:10,720
that he brought of the fruit of the ground

227
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:12,679
an offering unto the Lord,

228
00:13:12,679 --> 00:13:15,600
but Abel's offering was much different.

229
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:17,360
The Bible tells us that Abel,

